    <title>关于Error Spawn failed的问题</title>
    <link href="/2021/03/19/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EError%20Spawn%20failed%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2021/03/19/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EError%20Spawn%20failed%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="时隔一年没碰博客突然发现我博客上传不了了"><a href="#时隔一年没碰博客突然发现我博客上传不了了" class="headerlink" title="时隔一年没碰博客突然发现我博客上传不了了??!"></a>时隔一年没碰博客突然发现我博客上传不了了??!</h2><p>出现了这样的报错</p><pre><code>fatal: unable to access &#39;https://github.com/*******************************.github.io.git/&#39;: Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed outFATAL &#123;  err: Error: Spawn failed      at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; (C:\Users\*******************************\node_modules\hexo-deployer-git\node_modules\hexo-util\lib\spawn.js:51:21)      at ChildProcess.emit (events.js:315:20)      at ChildProcess.cp.emit (C:\Users\*******************************\node_modules\cross-spawn\lib\enoent.js:34:29)      at Process.ChildProcess._handle.onexit (internal/child_process.js:277:12) &#123;    code: 128  &#125;&#125; Something&#39;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: %s https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</code></pre><p><strong>啊这?</strong></p><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/03/18/6RKcTA.jpg" width="50%" height="50%"  /><p>后来病急乱投医直接搜索<br><strong>err: Error: Spawn failed</strong><br>一看啊,各种操作都有,都试了后<br>全部木大<br>后来自己仔细一想<br>今年好像github上不去了<br><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2021/03/19/6fSy8A.jpg"><br>我直接代理<br>不出所料直接成功<br>后来发现<br><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2021/03/19/6fSObT.jpg" alt="见黄色标记"><br>原来真正的原因写得清清楚楚<br><em>fatal: unable to access github</em><br>这个故事告诉我们要学好英语</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
